videos.description: Chol Marial makes a huge impact right away in his collegiate debut as the 7-foot-2 Maryland big man slams home a putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marial's first Maryland points come on a big putback jam) 2019/12/29

videos.headline: Marial's first Maryland points come on a big putback jam

videos.description: Darryl Morsell breaks down the Bryant defense, then dishes it to Chol Marial for the easy slam.
